{"id":148811,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/《顾蔚专栏》香港人民币ipo的投资者应该以史为鉴/","date":"2011-04-28T13:59:00Z","modified":"2011-04-28T13:59:00Z","title":"《顾蔚专栏》香港人民币IPO的投资者应该以史为鉴","content":"<p>路透香港4月26日电&#8212;中国喜欢搞金融实验,但不见得每次都成功.最近的人民币创新可能就是其中之一.以汇贤地产信托领头的香港人民币计价股票,让人回想起早被遗忘的为外资设计的B股市场.投资者在准备好下注汇贤以及後续的人民币计价股票时,应当以史为鉴.<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cn.reuters.feedsportal.com/c/33087/f/535380/s/1478b77c/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E3%80%8A%E9%A1%BE%E8%94%9A%E4%B8%93%E6%A0%8F%E3%80%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B8%81IPO%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E8%80%85%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%BA%E9%89%B4&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fcn.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FcolumnistNews%2FidCNCHINA-4217120110428%3FfeedType%3DRSS%26feedName%3DcolumnistNews\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/04/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E3%80%8A%E9%A1%BE%E8%94%9A%E4%B8%93%E6%A0%8F%E3%80%8B%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B8%81IPO%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E8%80%85%E5%BA%94%E8%AF%A5%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%BA%E9%89%B4&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fcn.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FcolumnistNews%2FidCNCHINA-4217120110428%3FfeedType%3DRSS%26feedName%3DcolumnistNews\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/04/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101090511000/u/31/f/535380/c/33087/s/1478b77c/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101090511000/u/31/f/535380/c/33087/s/1478b77c/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://cn.reuters.feedsportal.com/c/33087/f/535380/s/1478b77c/mf.gif\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http: